# 🌦️ Weather App  

### 🛠️ Technologies: HTML, Tailwind, JavaScript, API  

### ✨ Features
- 🔍 Search any city worldwide  
- 🌡️ Real-time temperature (C°/F°)  
- 💧 Humidity & 🌬️ wind speed  
- 📱 Fully responsive design  
- 🌙 Dark/Light mode  

